	<h3 class="title"><a href="/291172#comment-3405732" class="active">Sorry …..but if I were your professor in Liberty class</a></h3>
    <div class="submitted active">Submitted by <a href="/user/17075" title="View user profile.">Goldspan</a> on Sun, 05/11/2014 - 21:27.  <a class="permalink" href="/comment/3405732">Permalink</a></div>
