	<h3 class="title"><a href="/291172#comment-3127540" class="active">The "golden mean"...</a></h3>
    <div class="submitted banned">Submitted by <a href="/user/41039" title="View user profile.">NowOrNever</a> on Sat, 07/06/2013 - 14:13.  <a class="permalink" href="/comment/3127540">Permalink</a></div>
	<div class="content">
     <p>...is a lame attempt to rationalize the practical necessity for cooperation between conservatives and libertarians. It is laughably flawed. Do not build the libertarian-conservative coalition on that quicksand, build it on a practical understanding that cooperation benefits both parties.</p>
<p>P.S. The author also does not understand anarcho-capitalism.</p>
