	<h3 class="title"><a href="/291172#comment-3127206" class="active">Lawrence W. Reed on The Golden Mean</a></h3>
    <div class="submitted active">Submitted by <a href="/user/1" title="View user profile.">Michael Nystrom</a> on Sat, 07/06/2013 - 01:21.  <a class="permalink" href="/comment/3127206">Permalink</a></div>
